__SqlaTable__.sql:
select distinct 
name as "Gender"
from public.hm_ret_gender_dim

select 
'Year of Entry' as "DynamicDimension"
UNION 
select 
'Year of Study'
UNION 
select 
'Gender'
UNION 
select 
'Federal Cohort'
UNION 
select 
'Ethnicity'
UNION 
select 
'Enrollment Status'
UNION 
select 
'Age Group'
UNION 
select 
'ACT score'
UNION 
select 
'Took Remedial course(s)'
UNION 
select 
'High School GPA'
UNION 
select 
'Pell Recipient (1st year)'

select 
t6.degreegroup as "Program"
from public.hm_ret_degreegroup_dim t6
order by 1

select 
{{ "\"" + " ', '".join(filter_values('DynamicDimension')) + "\""}} as "Dimension",
--x."Gender" as "Dimension",
x."Year of Entry",
cast(x."Year of Study" as text),
x."Gender",
coalesce(x."Federal Cohort", 'No Cohort') as "Federal Cohort",
x."Ethnicity" as "Ethnicity",
x."Enrollment Status",
x."Age Group",
x."Credits taken, First fall",
x."Residency Status",
x."GPA credits, pre-Entry",
x."ACT score",
x."Took Remedial course(s)",
x."High School GPA",
x."Pell Recipient (1st year)",
x."Cohort term",
x."Attendance",
x."Dual / Summer enrollment",
x."First generation",
x."Math Prep",
x."English Prep",
x."Program",
count(distinct case when x.enrolflag=1 then x.studentenrollmentperiodid else null end ) as "Enrolled Count",
count(distinct case when x.graduationflag=1 then x.studentenrollmentperiodid else null end ) as "Graduated Count",
count(distinct x.studentenrollmentperiodid ) as total
from 

(select
t1.studentid,
t1.studentenrollmentperiodid,
t45.year as "Year of Entry",
t44.year as "Year of Study", 
t9.name as "Gender", 
concat(t6.degreegroup,'-',t7.name) as "Federal Cohort", -- Revisit , t7.code = F,H,L,Q
t8.name as "Ethnicity",
t7.name as  "Enrollment Status",
case 
		when t1.age < 17 then '<17' 
		when t1.age >= 18 and t1.age <= 23 then '18-23' 
		when t1.age >= 24 and t1.age <= 29 then '24-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 and t1.age <= 35 then '30-35' 
		when t1.age >= 36 and t1.age <= 40 then '36-40'
		when t1.age >= 41 and t1.age <= 45 then '41-45'
		when t1.age >= 46 and t1.age <= 50 then '46-50'
		else '>50' end as "Age Group",

case 
		when t1.studenttermcredithoursattempted  < 12 then '<12' 
		when t1.studenttermcredithoursattempted >= 12 and t1.studenttermcredithoursattempted <= 14 then '12-14' 
		when t1.studenttermcredithoursattempted > 14 then '>14' end as "Credits taken, First fall",
		
'' as  "Residency Status", -- Placeholder, no column in DB
t1.studenttermpreentrygpacredits as "GPA credits, pre-Entry", -- all null values

case 
		when t1.act_score <= 20 then 'ACT 20 or less' 
		when t1.act_score >= 21 and t1.act_score <= 25 then 'ACT 21-25' 
		when t1.act_score >= 26 and t1.act_score <= 30 then 'ACT 26-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 then 'ACT 30 or more'
		else 'No ACT' end  as "ACT score",

case 
when t1.remedialflag = 1 then 'Remedial' 
when t1.remedialflag = 0 then 'No Remedial' else 'Undefined' end as "Took Remedial course(s)", 

case 
when t1.hsgpa >= 0.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 1.99 then '0.00-1.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 2.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 2.49 then '2.00-2.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 2.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 2.99 then '2.50-2.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 3.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 3.49 then '3.00-3.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 3.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 3.99 then '3.50-3.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 4.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 4.49 then '4.00-4.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 4.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 4.99 then '4.50-4.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 5.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 5.49 then '5.00-5.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 5.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 5.99 then '5.50-5.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 6.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 6.49 then '6.00-6.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 6.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 6.99 then '6.50-6.99'
when t1.hsgpa >= 7.00 and t1.hsgpa <= 7.49 then '7.00-7.49'
when t1.hsgpa >= 7.50 and t1.hsgpa <= 7.99 then '7.50-7.99'
else '>=8.00' end as "High School GPA",


case when t1.pellrecepient = 'N' then 'No' when t1.pellrecepient = 'Y' then 'Yes' else 'Undefined'
end as "Pell Recipient (1st year)",

t3.name as "Cohort term",
t1.attendance_percentage as "Attendance", -- Full time, part time values in PPT
t1.dualenrollmentflag as "Dual / Summer enrollment",
t1.firstgenerationflag as "First generation",
t1.mathprepflag as "Math Prep",
t1.englishprepflag as "English Prep",
t6.degreegroup as "Program",
t1.state ,
max(t1.graduationflag) as graduationflag,
max(t1.enrolflag) as enrolflag 
from ret_stdnt_fact t1
left outer join public.hm_ret_terms_dim t3 on (t1.cohort_term_key =t3.skey)
left outer join public.hm_ret_year_dim t44 on t1.year_of_study_key =t44.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_year_dim t45 on t1.year_of_entry_key =t45.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_degreegroup_dim t6 on t1.degreegroup_key = t6.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_enrlstat_dim t7 on t1.enrollstatus_key = t7.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_ethnicities_dim t8 on t1.ethnicities_key = t8.skey
left outer join public.hm_ret_gender_dim t9 on t1.gender_key = t9.skey

where 
--t45.year > 2017 and t45.year <> 2023
t1.year_of_entry_key > 118 and t1.year_of_study_key < 124
group by 
t1.studentid,
t1.studentenrollmentperiodid,
t44.year,
t45.year,
t9.name,
concat(t6.degreegroup,' ',t7.name),
t8.name,
t7.name,
t1.age,
t1.studenttermcredithoursattempted,
t1.studenttermpreentrygpacredits,
t1.act_score,
t1.remedialflag,
t1.hsgpa,
t1.pellrecepient,
t3.name,
t1.attendance_percentage,
t1.dualenrollmentflag,
t1.firstgenerationflag,
t1.mathprepflag,
t1.englishprepflag,
t6.degreegroup,
t1.state ) x
group by
{{ "\"" + " ', '".join(filter_values('DynamicDimension')) + "\""}},
--x."Gender",
x."Year of Entry",
cast(x."Year of Study" as text),
x."Gender",
coalesce(x."Federal Cohort", 'No Cohort'),
x."Ethnicity",
x."Enrollment Status",
x."Age Group",
x."Credits taken, First fall",
x."Residency Status",
x."GPA credits, pre-Entry",
x."ACT score",
x."Took Remedial course(s)",
x."High School GPA",
x."Pell Recipient (1st year)",
x."Cohort term",
x."Attendance",
x."Dual / Summer enrollment",
x."First generation",
x."Math Prep",
x."English Prep",
x."Program"

select 
name as  "Enrollment Status"
from 
public.hm_ret_enrlstat_dim

select distinct 
year as "Year of Entry",
cast(year as text) as "Year of Study"
from public.hm_ret_year_dim
where year >= 2017 and   year <= 2022

select
DISTINCT 

case 
when t1.remedialflag = 1 then 'Remedial' 
when t1.remedialflag = 0 then 'No Remedial' else 'Undefined' end as "Took Remedial course(s)"

from ret_stdnt_fact t1
order by 1

select distinct name as "Ethnicity" from public.hm_ret_ethnicities_dim

select
DISTINCT 

case 
		when t1.age < 17 then '<17' 
		when t1.age >= 18 and t1.age <= 23 then '18-23' 
		when t1.age >= 24 and t1.age <= 29 then '24-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 and t1.age <= 35 then '30-35' 
		when t1.age >= 36 and t1.age <= 40 then '36-40'
		when t1.age >= 41 and t1.age <= 45 then '41-45'
		when t1.age >= 46 and t1.age <= 50 then '46-50'
		else '>50' end as "Age Group"



from ret_stdnt_fact t1

select
DISTINCT 

case 
		when t1.act_score <= 20 then 'ACT 20 or less' 
		when t1.act_score >= 21 and t1.act_score <= 25 then 'ACT 21-25' 
		when t1.act_score >= 26 and t1.act_score <= 30 then 'ACT 26-29' 
		when t1.age >= 30 then 'ACT 30 or more'
		else 'No ACT' end  as "ACT score"

from ret_stdnt_fact t1
order by 1
